{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 200°C. Line a baking tray (30 x 40 cm) with baking paper and set aside.","Place oil, onion, garlic and chilli into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then sauté <b>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Add cayenne pepper, paprika, canned tomatoes and salt. Place Varoma dish into position and weigh potatoes into it. Secure Varoma lid and cook <b>20 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma aside and <strong>insert measuring cup<\/strong>, then blend <b>30 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer sauce into a thermal serving bowl or other large bowl and cover to keep warm.","Place potatoes onto prepared baking tray and top with sliced chorizo. Bake for 15 minutes (200°C). Remove from oven and stir potatoes and chorizo to ensure even cooking. Return tray to the oven and bake for a further 25-30 minutes (200°C), or until potatoes are golden and chorizo is sizzling.","Transfer potatoes and chorizo into a serving bowl and serve sauce warm on the side."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1 tbsp olive oil","60 g red onion","2 garlic cloves","½ - 1 fresh red chilli, deseeded if preferred and cut into halves","1 pinch ground cayenne pepper","1 pinch ground smoked paprika","400 g canned chopped tomatoes","¼ - ½ tsp sea salt, to taste","800 - 850 g small potatoes, peeled and cut pieces (2-3 cm)","3 chorizo (approx. 500 g), thinly sliced"]}],"id":"r82174","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-vjhAaOis_cY\/XZMzEQHXFKI\/AAAAAAAAas4\/srjpwNlWRF0FXKbxeoBbGAe25U7uQbj2QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_UvFVcj5z2X7ii-1I.png","title":"Patatas bravas with chorizo","publishedAt":"2015-05-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"10.5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13 g","calories":"828 kJ \/ 197 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking tray (30 x 40 cm), baking paper, thermal serving bowl or other large bowl, oven","hintsAndTricks":["This is a classic tapas dish served throughout Spain. Enjoy as the start to a Tapas themed menu or simply as a nibble at your next party."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 20m","10 portions"]}